      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "そう……かな？",
      "startTime": 19.0022448857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.5829250653
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02-rik003.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ次は……って、あれ？",
      "startTime": 21.5829250653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "梨子ちゃん、どうしたの……って、わっ\n怜ちゃんに、遙子さん……？",
      "startTime": 28.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、今日はこの辺りで\nお仕事の打ち合わせがあるって……",
      "startTime": 33.6424185752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.951995023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "梨子ちゃん……ごめんなさい\n策が裏目に出た……逃げよう……！",
      "startTime": 39.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4248.0049770000005,
          "startTime": 41.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.1383895237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
