      "text": "今度はさっきの、逆……",
      "startTime": 54.705057462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.1756683667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "木を隠すなら森の中……人込みの中なら\nかえってバレにくいから……",
      "startTime": 61.4666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.8245796521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02-rik006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどね。確かにここなら\n近くに知り合いがいても……あれ？",
      "startTime": 66.288888043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.9912463188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02-rik007.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか周りから視線を感じるような……？",
      "startTime": 69.9912463188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.9912463188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02-rik008.m4a",
      "text": "あ。雫ちゃん、サニピのファンの人みたいよ？\n……え？　サニピのライブを観てた！？",
      "startTime": 77.8912463188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.3579129855
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02-rik009.m4a",
      "text": "ゲストで出演した私のことも覚えてる……？\nあわわ、あ、ありがとうございます……！",
      "startTime": 84.9912463188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.0912463188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "人が……一杯集まってきた……！",
      "startTime": 88.0912463188,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 88.0912463188
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.4924480915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02-rik010.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、こういう時はどうすれば……！？\nTシャツにサインを書けばいいの！？",
      "startTime": 94.7924480915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
