      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "それはたぶん少数派……！　それに\n一回書き出したら……もう、収拾がつかなくなる……！",
      "startTime": 100.2000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
